data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER, BRING US AN OFFER! Don’t miss out on an opportunity to call the desirable Cedar Creek Village community of Mount Juliet home! This fully-renovated home is perfect for lake-lovers, located just minutes from Cedar Creek Marina and picturesque Old Hickory Lake. Step into the large family room with soaring ceilings, gas fireplace, and an abundance of natural light. The nearby kitchen features brand new stainless appliances, new granite tops, and is open to the breakfast nook with bay window. Primary suite offers tray ceiling with large windows, walk-in closet, and spacious bathroom. Step onto the back deck running the span of the house, and overlooking a private backyard!
